data.description: READY FOR IMMEDIATE MOVE-IN!!! NEWLY RENOVATED! Beautiful 4/2.5/2 home has brand new tile flooring & carpet throughout. Entry way leads to a large living area with a view of the vast backyard that's perfect for entertaining, family fun, or simply retreating from the day's demands. Breakfast area has updated lighting with beautiful seeded glass cones that appear throughout the home. All new appliances in the kitchen. Master bedroom has a massive walk-in closet with built-in shelving & an extended area for storage. Master bath has been updated with new lighting, fixtures, framed mirror, counter-top, & separate tub and shower. Game room offers a bench seat & connects to a loft with a refreshing aerial view of the large living room beneath. Roomy secondary bedrooms have ample room to suit your needs. Upstairs bathroom has updated lighting, fixtures, & counters. Brand new fence. Gorgeous lighted walking trails. Plenty of space for whoever will call this beauty home! This one is a must see!!
